                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7182" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1796</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8598 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">漳州片仔癀轻资产运营转型之路：百年名药“避重就轻”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Way of Zhangzhou Pien Tze Huang’s Light Asset Operation Transformation:A Century Old Famous Medicine for Avoiding the Heavy and Taking the Light</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">代文，彭逸飞，张宇婧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">漳州片仔癀药业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻资产；运营模式；产业链 </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Light assets; Operation mode; Industrial chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">片仔癀距今已有五百年的历史，是当之无愧的百年“老字号”。老字号的“老”在于传统和资历，但也意味着难以创新。面对时代的创新潮流，漳州片仔癀药业股份有限公司原董事长刘建顺于 2013 年上任之际，提出“一核两翼”轻资产运营战略导向，开启漳州片仔癀轻资产运营转型之路。在 2021 年的年报中“一核两翼”战略进一步延伸为“多核驱动,双向发展”，这也标志着漳州片仔癀的轻资产运营开始更加深入的发展。轻资产运营的概念最开始出现于互联网企业，漳州片仔癀这一中药企业，基于行业发展变化与企业自身的特性，选择摒弃重资产老路，开始探索轻资产运营之路。本案例通过对片仔癀轻资产转型措施的阐述，分析其轻资产转型的效果，引导学生思考轻资产这一运营模式的在不同行业的应用方式，以及轻资产模式如何将企业资源进行整合，并将如何影响企业价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With a history of 500 years,PienTzeHuang is a well deserved &quot;time-honored brand&quot;. The &quot;old&quot; of time-honored brands lies in their tradition and qualifications, but it also means that they are difficult to innovate. In the face of the innovation trend of the times,Liu Jianshun,the former chairman of Zhangzhou PienTzeHuang Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd., put forward the strategic orientation of &quot;one core and two wings&quot; light asset operation when he took office in 2013, opening the way for Zhangzhou PienTzeHuang to light asset operation. In the 2021 annual report, the strategy of &quot;one core and two wings&quot; is further extended to &quot;multi-core driven, two-way development&quot;, which also marks that the asset light operation of Zhangzhou PienTzeHuang has begun to develop more deeply. The concept of asset light operation first appeared in Internet enterprises. Based on the development and changes of the industry and the characteristics of the enterprise itself, Zhangzhou PienTzeHuang, a traditional Chinese medicine enterprise, chose to abandon the old way of asset light operation and began to explore the way of asset light operation. This case analyzes the effect of the asset light transformation by elaborating the asset light transformation measures of PienTzeHuang, guides students to think about the application of the asset light operation mode in different industries, and how the asset light mode integrates enterprise resources and affects enterprise value.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">轻资产运营模式；微笑曲线理论；全产业链理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
